            {
               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nThis game is a continuation of a previous game, in which we performed the multiplication of a number with tens and units by another that has only units (<htcite0>). Therefore, we suggest you practice with that game before proceeding, to understand the multiplication steps.",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "5edb2a2d-ea6e-47dc-b526-e9db86c06181",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
